          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " To detect protons emanating from the target, a",
                "0.16 cm water of NaI(Tl), covered with 13 mu-m",
                "aluminium foil and mounted on a Dumont 6291",
                "photomultiplier, was moved from port to port on a 23 cm",
                "diameter circle about the chamber axis."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The target, consisting of a thin layer of Be7O",
                "deposited on a 0.013 cm thick platinum disk, was",
                "prepared by chemical and physical separations of Be-7",
                "from lithium metal. The target was fairly uniform over",
                "a spot about 4 mm in diameter with a surface density of",
                "10**16 Be-7 atoms per cm2 and a total radioactivity of",
                "10 mc."
              ]
            }
          ],
